data.title: North Memorial Health – Maple Grove Hospital
data.meta_description: North Memorial Health – Maple Grove Hospital provides health care, the way it ought to be delivered, in the West Metro area.
data.text:
Fairview

Fairview's network of 5,000 providers, 56 clinics, 100+ specialties and 12 hospitals offers a full spectrum of health care services.

Metropolitan Neurosurgery, PA

Providers specializing in neurosurgical care of the brain, spine, and spinal cord on both a scheduled and emergency basis.

Twin Cities Plastic Surgery

Dr. Joe Gryskiewicz has expertise performing a wide range of cosmetic and reconstructive procedures, serving the Minneapolis and St. Paul areas for over 30 years.

Wayzata Children’s Clinic

Wayzata Children's Clinic board certified Pediatricians specialize in ongoing pediatric care from infancy through adolescence. Same Day Sick Visits walk-ins available in Minnetonka & Chaska.

Minnesota Gastroenterology

Minnesota Gastroenterology specializes in the diagnosis and treatment of adults and children with GI disorders and has several convenient outpatient endoscopy centers and clinics.

Ness Plastic Surgery LLC

Guided by John A. Ness, M.D., our plastic surgery office provides a wide array of plastic surgery procedures. We are committed to providing excellence in all that we do.

Minneapolis Clinic of Neurology

Minneapolis Clinic of Neurology's mission is to provide exceptional, personalized neurologic care. For services and locations, visit us online.

Respiratory Consultants

An independent group of physicians committed to promoting lung and sleep health, and treating a variety of pulmonary and sleep problems using state of the art technology.

Minnesota Spine Institute

A surgical center built on excellence through education, research and applied results using today's latest advancements in spine surgery technologies including minimally invasive spine procedures.

Mesna Plastic Surgery

Mesna Plastic Surgery offers a broad range of surgical options, minimally invasive treatments, and nonsurgical treatments for cosmetic enhancement of the face, body, breasts and skin.

McCue Plastic Surgery PA

As a board-certified plastic surgeon, Jonathan McCue, M.D., is available for both cosmetic and reconstructive plastic surgery to patients in the entire Twin Cities metro area.

Minnesota Bone & Joint Specialists

Minnesota Bone & Joint Specialists' orthopaedic surgeons and staff are committed to excellence. We pledge to provide the highest quality orthopaedics care possible.

Oakdale Ear, Nose & Throat

Oakdale Ear, Nose & Throat Clinic is committed to your health and well being, treating allergies, hearing loss, sinus disorders - and many other ENT conditions.

Platinum Health LLC

Dr. Paul N. Yakshe at Platinum Health offers a broad spectrum of gastroenterology services to help you maintain a healthy digestive system.

TK Plastic Surgery LLC

Kayan Plastic Surgery is robust plastic surgery practice doing cosmetic breast and body procedures, fat grafting, breast reconstruction and gender confirmation surgery.

Minnesota Urology PA

Minnesota Urology is a center of excellence for men and women, with 31 clinic locations serving patients in Minneapolis, St. Paul and areas throughout Minnesota and western Wisconsin.

Partners in Pediatrics Ltd

At Partners in Pediatrics, we provide health care for children and adolescents in partnership with their parents. Our goal is to understand the diverse needs of children and their families.

Clinic Sofia OBGYN

A leading OBGYN clinic with locations in Maple Grove and Edina known for its personalized approach to healthcare.

Voyage Healthcare

Voyage Healthcare, formally known as North Clinic, is an independently owned, multi-specialty practice. Voyage Healthcare provides the positive healthcare experience you deserve through every stage of life. Locations are located in the northwest metro.

Midwest Spine & Brain Institute

Midwest Spine & Brain Institute is dedicated to restoring lives affected by spine and brain injury, disease, and disorder.

Summit Orthopedics

Providing comprehensive orthopedic and spine care supporting healthy, active lifestyles. Offering same-day spine appointments, sub-specialty clinics, therapy, and minimally-invasive surgery.

Oakdale Obstetrics & Gynecology

Comprehensive pregnancy and gynecology care for women in all stages of life. Our award-winning team includes ObGyn doctors, GYN surgeons, midwives, and nurse practitioners.

James A. Hoffman, MD – Cosmetic & Plastic Surgery PA

A cosmetic plastic surgery practice dedicated to excellence and enhancing your appearance and self-image. Dr. Hoffman is trained in all aspects of Plastic Surgery.

Minneapolis Vascular Physicians

Minneapolis Vascular Physicians are experts in vascular care, dedicated to providing high-quality, timely and compassionate care to improve the lives of our patients.

Emergency Physicians Professional Association (EPPA)

Emergency Physicians Professional Association (EPPA) has been providing physician/APC staffing in emergency departments across Minnesota since 1969.

Park Nicollet Clinic

Providing the care to help keep your family healthy is our top priority - from birth and throughout life, we’re here for you.

South Lake Pediatrics

At South Lake Pediatrics, you’re the center of our universe. It’s our mission to provide patients with the highest quality care in a friendly, personal and compassionate environment.

Minnesota Neonatal Physicians

Minnesota Neonatal Physicians provide state-of-the-art diagnosis, treatment and follow-up care for premature and medically fragile neonates.

Park Nicollet – Women’s Services Clinic

Whatever you’re experiencing - pregnancy to menopause, our highly-skilled and compassionate doctors and nurse practitioners will attend to your individual needs and preferences.

SP Plastic Surgery

Dr. Peng is trained in aesthetic surgery, hand surgery, and reconstruction of wounds related to cancer and trauma to restore form, function, and beauty to each patient.

Northwest Family Clinics

A whole life care approach; we are with our patient’s from birth until geriatric years.
